title: UNLEASHED UNIVERSE S00CH01 World Heroes E02 The terrible truth
description:
In this thrilling sequel episode we discover a terrible truth, and the fight for justice continues as the warriors of good enter a new phase, this will change everything. The future of mankind is on the brink of a new age, and there will be no turning back from where this is headed. 

This series is just getting started, there is so much more in store, where and how this all comes together will surprise you till it's shocking and unexpected bigger picture emerges from what we have seen, and yet not seen.... keeping in line with the grand vision of the upcoming Marvel/DC crossover, while throwing surprise after surprise - with it's twists and turns, and the unexpected crossovers that are known only to the hardcore superhero fans that know the full updated story of the characters, the crossovers (cartoon and comic story accurate), and their backstories, if you have never seem those mediums or their story lines ... you will be delightfully and even shockingly surprised where this goes..... But even those who know all the facts - still have a few surprises awaiting them - this is the beginning of a mega journey through the heroes and the villains.....   and even the ones in between!!!


2 of 8 in chapter 1 of many
many chapters make a season, and I have seasons upon seasons of this story....

enjoy this unique take on the superhero universes we know and love
